'''p7zip''' is a command-line port of [http://www.7-zip.org/ 7-Zip] for POSIX complaint systems such as Unix, MacOS X, BeOS, and Amiga. Created by Igor Pavlov, 7-Zip compression type uses one of the highest compression ratios currently available. Since version 4.10 it supports little and big endian machines. 

